name: Spices Coffee Shop
description: Located on the ground floor, SPICES restaurant serves authentic Indonesian cuisine, highlighted by its famous Sop Buntut (Oxtail Soup). In addition to the locally inspired menu, diners may enjoy a creative fusion of Asian and Western specialties. Foods are served from live cooking stalls, buffet and a la carte. Accommodating up to 115 people in indoor and semi-outdoor settings, SPICES is suitable for corporate gatherings, family brunches, and meetings with friends.
